from Port&s;mouth, 20th July, 1710."</P>
<P>"Letter from one M. Cook,<NOTE PLACE="marg">16.</NOTE> recommending a Mr. Ward to his charity, Ver|&s;ailles,
21&s;t July, 1710."</P>
<P><PB N="679" REF="705">
"D. Boyd to lord Middleton,<NOTE PLACE="marg">D. N. vol iii. 4to. No. 20.</NOTE> about his and companion's con&s;inement, for &s;ome
mi&s;demeanour about the ca&s;tle of St. Germains."</P>
<P>"A father John&s;on to the Queen,<NOTE PLACE="marg">21.</NOTE> about a &s;py; and extract of a letter from
