<P>The &s;everal papers concerning Sir Robert Long,<NOTE PLACE="marg">A. L. I folio, page 144&mdash;166 and 189&mdash;201.</NOTE> Sir Richard Greenville, and
Peter Ma&s;&s;onet's accu&s;ation of Sir Edward's Hyde's corre&s;pondence with Cromwell,
