<P>Extracts and papers,<NOTE PLACE="marg">356&mdash;360.</NOTE> which contain nothing material.</P>
<P>Be&s;ides the papers of which a li&s;t is given in this Appendix, and tho&s;e few
which are publi&s;hed in the preceding volumes, or to which Mr. Carte him&s;elf ro|&s;ers
